dev-master.name: fountain/cache
dev-master.description: Caching library with same interface for popular drivers

suggest.ext-apc: Lets to use APC as driver (for php > 5.5 install APCu)
suggest.ext-redis: Lets to use Redis as driver
suggest.ext-couchbase: Lets to use CouchBase as driver
suggest.ext-memcache: Lets to use Memcache as cache driver
suggest.ext-memcached: Lets to use Memcached as cache driver
suggest.ext-xcache: Lets to use XCache as cache driver
suggest.ext-wincache: Lets to use Wincache as cache driver
